# Bhanks Base Project

A full on-chain ecosystem built on [Base](https://base.org).

## What's included
- **BhanksToken** — ERC-20 token (BHNK)
- **BhanksNFT** — ERC-721 NFT collection
- **BhanksStaking** — Stake BHNK, earn rewards
- **BhanksDAO** — Token-weighted governance

## Tech stack
- Base L2 blockchain
- OnchainKit — React components
- Next.js — Frontend
- Hardhat — Smart contracts
- wagmi + viem — Wallet connection

## Status
In active development. Follow [@bhanks_crypt](https://x.com/bhanks_crypt)

## Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Bhanks434/bhanks-base-project
cd bhanks-base-project
npm install
cp .env.example .env
npm run dev
```